author: filmaj
msg: BlackBerry PhoneGap updated, lots of changes. Changed from BrowserContentManager to Browser.Field object as browser wrapper. Started to port all PhoneGap API calls to cookies (since at the moment we cant catch gap:// URI calls properly).

author: filmaj
msg: PhoneGap Blackberry working with proper Blackberry browser rendering! Changed PhoneGap Blackberry approach from using BrowserContentManager class to a Field class object. Much more low-level definition/control over HttpConnection object associated with PhoneGap. Still needs some work: cookies need to be enabled and PhoneGap callbacks hooked in properly to cookies.
